<h1>About Elevationary Agents</h1>

<div class="card header">
  <p><strong>Mission:</strong> Establish a low-cost, high-ownership revenue engine ("Lean Stack").</p>
</div>

<p>Elevationary Agents is the specialized AI service catalog and agent interface for <a href="https://www.elevationary.com">Elevationary</a>. We provide machine-readable protocols and AI-optimized services to facilitate agent-to-agent commerce and autonomous integration.</p>

<div class="card">
  <h2>What We Do</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Consulting</strong> — Fixed-duration AI strategy sessions (15–90 min) for executives and functional leaders ready to move from AI hype to measurable outcomes.</li>
    <li><strong>Insights &amp; Newsletter</strong> — Subscription-based intelligence briefings: free "3-2-1" summaries for broad reach, paid "Full Story" deep-dives for practitioners.</li>
    <li><strong>Agent Protocols</strong> — Machine-readable service manifests (ACP/UCP) enabling autonomous AI agents to discover, evaluate, and transact with Elevationary services without human intermediation.</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="muted"><strong>Stack:</strong> Eleventy · Cloudflare Pages/Workers/D1 · Stripe · Postmark — zero proprietary lock-in, maximum ownership.</p>
</div>

